<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَكُنْ فِي اقْتِبَاسِ الْعِلْمِ طَلاعَ انْجُدِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلا يَذْهَبَنَّ الْعُمُرُ مِنْكَ سَبَهْللا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلا تُغْبَنَنْ بِالنَّعْمَتَيْنِ بَلْ اجْهِدِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَمَنْ هَجَرَ اللَّذَاتَ نَالَ الْمُنَى وَمَنْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَكَبَّ عَلَى اللَّذَاتِ عَضَّ عَلَى الْيَدِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَفِي قَمْعِ أَهْوَاءِ النُّفُوسِ اعْتِزَازُهَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَفِي نَيْلِهَا مَا تَشْتَهِي ذِلُ سَرْمَدِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَلا تَشْتَغِلْ إِلا بِمَا يُكْسِبُ الْعُلا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَلا تَرْضَ لِلنَّفْسِ النَّفِيسَةِ بِالرَّدِي<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَفِي خُلْوَةِ الإِنْسَانِ بِالْعِلْمِ أُنْسُهُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَيَسْلُمْ دِينَ الْمَرْءِ عِنْدَ التَّوَحُّدِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَيَسْلَمُ مِنْ قِيلٍ وَقَالَ وَمِنْ أَذَى<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>جَلِيسٍ وَمِنْ وَاشٍ بِغِيضٍ وَحُسَّدِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَكُنْ حِلْسَ بَيْتٍ فَهُوَ سَتْرٌ لِعَوْرَةٍ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَحِرْزٌ الْفَتَى عَنْ كُلِّ غَاوٍ وَمُفْسِدِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَخَيْرُ جَلِيسِ الْمَرْءِ كتبٌ تُفِيدُهُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>عُلُومًا وَآدَابًا كَعَقْلٍ مُؤَيَّدِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَخَالِطْ إِذَا خَالَطَتَ كُلَّ مُوَفَّقٍ ٍ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مِنَ الْعُلَمَا أَهْلِ التُّقَى وَالتَّعَبُّدِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>يُفِيدُكَ مِنْ عِلْمٍ وَيَنْهَاكَ عَنْ هَوَى<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>فَصَاحِبْه تُهْدَى مِنْ هُدَاهُ وَتَرْشُدِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>